  "name": "Morrison VAD Hemolysis CFD — Minimal Profile Credibility Package",
  "description": "This Unit of Assurance documents the simulation credibility evidence for CFD-based hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. The model has been applied in clinical research settings to support ventricular assist device design decisions, and all thirteen ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been evaluated against the applicable model risk level. Credibility activities were conducted by an independent assessment team; the aggregate evidence is judged sufficient for the intended analytical purpose. No structured Context of Use object is provided under this minimal profile submission; the intended-use scope is conveyed only through the narrative description above.",
