      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric (e.g., validation metric u_val) computed for each QoI with statistical confidence intervals reported.",
      "rationale": "Validation metric computed for pressure-flow characteristic and velocity fields with 95% confidence intervals; hemolysis index comparison relies on point estimates only, lacking propagated experimental uncertainty."
