      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Direct traceability established between each validated QoI and the device safety/performance endpoint.",
      "rationale": "Pressure head and flow rate are directly relevant; the hemolysis index is a surrogate metric whose link to in-vivo red blood cell damage has not been formally quantified for this pump geometry."
